                     <interp inst="t18310630-247-person1807" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . A sack of soot is worth 3s., and a sack 1s.; I have lost a sack.</p>
               <p>Two witnesses attended to prove an alibi, but their evidence did not relate to the day on which the robbery was committed.</p>
